.span3
  #sidebar
    #goodbrews-b= image_tag "b.png"
    %h1 Welcome!

.span9
  #content
    .filler
    %h1 goodbre.ws

    #about
      %p
        Welcome to goodbre.ws, a web application for beer lovers who want to try something new.
        Register an account and tell us what beer you like and what beer you don't, and we'll
        do the rest! The more you tell us, the easier it will be for us to make more accurate
        recommendations for you. When you're ready, sign up using the link above to get one
        step closer to trying new beer!

    .tabbable
      %ul.nav.nav-tabs
        %li.active= link_to "Top 10 Beers", "#top-beers", 'data-toggle' => 'tab'
      .tab-content
        #top-beers.tab-pane.active
          %table.table.table-striped
            %tr
              %th Name
              %th ABV
              %th Style
              %th Brewery
              %th
          - Beer.top(10).each do |beer|
            %tr
              %td= beer.name
              %td= beer.abv
              %td= beer.style.name
              %td= beer.brewery.name
              %td= render :partial => 'beers/buttons', :locals => { :beer => beer }
